description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/Parashare: Creating Black Holes and Capturing Souls Edition with Beer City Bruiser!! 

It has been a perplexing week to say the least! A week where what you think you know isn't exactly is as it seems, Tim and Bruiser have gathered up the information and pertinent news stories and have them ready for you!

This week,  CERN is back at it again as they fire up the Large Hadron Collider... and they find something! The Government comes forward and clarifies Dr. Travis Taylor's role in it's alien hunting operation, and a man says his family won't visit him because his century year old haunted doll makes them ill and they are afraid!!
